This is a C extension for PHP that supplys very fast BB code parsing.

It can also ported to other languages. The C source files can used without any changes in C/C++ applications.

------------
Installation
------------
phpize
./configure
make
make install

----------
Known bugs
----------
It seems that something in the PHP wrapper is invalid. Got segfaults in production use somethimes.
When some PHP extension gurus are around somewhere...

-----
Usage
-----
Have a look at test.php and test.txt for PHP examples.
Or have a look at lib/ubb.c at main() function.
